A [[mining pool|Pooled_mining]].


##Reward distribution

* Pay-per-share (PPS) with 3% fee, current rate shown on website.

* Minimum payout is 0.01 BTC

* Pay for stale shares

* Handy payouts: BTC, Liberty Reserve, cell phone (Russia), Yandex.Money, QIWI, WebMoney.

##Features

* Full statistics (Real-time)
* Currency converter
* Reward calculator
* IP white list
* API in JSON format
* Teams
* Charts of currency rate
* Registration not required
* English and Russian interface
* Fast and responsible support
* List of [ frequently asked questions](https://50btc.com/faq)

